description:
Prophecy-minded Christians often debate whether Jesus will return at the beginning of the "7 years of Tribulation" (the pre-Trib view), or in the middle of the "7 years of Tribulation" (the mid-Trib view), or at the end of the "7 years of Tribulation" (the post-Trib view). But the larger question is: Does the Bible really teach "7 years of Tribulation” at all? Discover shocking facts straight from the Bible.
